04_IL17_in_lymph

Marta Casado-Pelaez

This script generates panels A, B, D, F and G of main figure 4.

Libraries:

library(Seurat)
library(ggplot2)
library(ggpubr)
library(cowplot)
library(dplyr)
library(ggrepel)
library(sccomp)
library(here)

Load data:

# Seurat object
lymphoid <- readRDS(here("data", "adult_aged", "lymphoid.RDS"))
lymphoid_subclustered <- readRDS(here("data", "adult_aged", "lymphoid_subclustered.RDS"))

# Sccomp object
sccomp_lymphoid <- readRDS(here("data", "adult_aged", "sccomp_lymphoid_subclusters.RDS"))

# Colors
col_lymphoid_subclusters <- readRDS(here("data", "col_lymphoid_subclusters.RDS"))


Main figure 4a

Idents(lymphoid) <- lymphoid$annotation
features <- c("Cd4+ Th" = "Il17f",
              "γδ T" = "Il17a",
              "γδ T" = "Il17f",
              "ILC" = "Il17a",
              "ILC" = "Il17f")

fp_plots <- features %>%
  purrr::imap(~Seurat::VlnPlot(object = lymphoid, 
                               features = .x, 
                               group.by = "condition", 
                               idents = .y, 
                               cols = c("lightgray", "red")) +
  labs(title = .y, subtitle = .x) +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5), 
        plot.subtitle = element_text(hjust = 0.5, face = "italic"),
        legend.position = "none")) 

gg <- ggpubr::ggarrange(plotlist = fp_plots, ncol = 5, nrow = 1)
gg

# save
ggsave(gg, file = here::here("figures", paste0("main_fig_4a.pdf")), 
         width = 17.5, height = 4.5)

Main figure 4b

umap <- Seurat::DimPlot(object = lymphoid_subclustered, 
                        reduction = 'umap', 
                        group.by = "gdt_cd4t_subclusters", 
                        cols = col_lymphoid_subclusters) +
  theme_void() +
  theme(legend.text = element_text(size = 14),
        plot.title = element_text(size = 14, hjust = 0.5),
        strip.text.x =element_text(size = 15)) +
  labs(title = "Subpopulation analysis of \n CD4+ Th and γδT cells")
umap

# save
file.name <- here::here("figures", "main_fig_4b.pdf")
ggsave(file = file.name, plot = umap, width = 8, height = 6)

Main figure 4d and 4f

plots <- sccomp::plot_summary(sccomp_lymphoid) 

plots$boxplot
## [[1]]

# save
file.name <-  here::here("figures", "main_fig_4d_f.pdf")
ggsave(file = file.name, width = 15, height = 8)

Main figure 4g

Idents(lymphoid) <- lymphoid$annotation
features <- c("Tmem176a",
              "Tmem176b")

fp_plots <- features %>%
  purrr::map(~Seurat::VlnPlot(lymphoid, 
                              features = .x, 
                              group.by = "condition", 
                              idents = "ILC", 
                              cols = c("lightgray", "red")) +
  labs(title = "ILC", subtitle = .x) +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5), 
        plot.subtitle = element_text(hjust = 0.5, face = "italic"),
        legend.position = "none")) 

gg <- ggpubr::ggarrange(plotlist = fp_plots, ncol = 2, nrow = 1)
gg

# save
ggsave(gg, file = here::here("figures", paste0("main_fig_4g.pdf")), 
         width = 7, height = 4.5)
